kamura A, Lagha M, Besse F. 2021. Tyramine induces dynamic RNP granule remodeling and translation activation in the <italic>Drosophila</italic> brain. <italic>eLife</italic> <bold>10</bold>:e65742. doi: <ext-link ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="http://dx.doi.org/10.7554/eLife.65742">10.7554/eLife.65742</ext-link>.</p><p>Published 23, April 2021</p></boxed-text><p>In the published article, Figure 2C inadvertently presented four times the image corresponding to the first time point (t=0) of the control movie. This has been corrected and the proper image sequence is now shown. No further changes were made to the text and figure legend. Please note that this correction does not affect the results and conclusions of the original paper.</p><p>The corrected Figure 2C is shown here:</p><fig id="fig1" position="float"><graphic mime-subtype="tiff" mimetype="image" xlink:href="elife-70755-fig1-v1.tif"/></fig><p>The originally published Figure 2C is also shown for reference:</p><fig id="fig2" position="float"><graphic mime-subtype="tiff" mimetype="image" xlink:href="elife-70755-fig2-v1.tif"/></fig><p>The article has been corrected accordingly.</p></body></article>